Package: geoMatch
Title: geoMatch
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Dan Runfola  <dan@danrunfola.com>, Ariel BenYishay <abenyishay@wm.edu>, Seth Goodman <sgoodman@aiddata.org>
Maintainer: Dan Runfola <dan@danrunfola.com>
Description: geoMatch improves models using spatial data for the purposes of causal inference by (a) adjusting for spatial spillover effects, and (b) leveraging MatchIt to select matched subsets of spatially defined treated and control locations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: sp
Depends: R (>= 3.0.1), MatchIt
Suggests: spdep
LazyData: true
LazyLoad: yes
URL: https://github.com/itpir/geo.match
BugReports: https://github.com/itpir/geo.match/issues
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
